<font size="28"><font face="ArmWrestler"><font color="#423330"><font size="40">Nohara</font></font></font></font>

29
00:01:19,970 --> 00:01:25,020
<font size="28">{\an1}<font face="ArmWrestler"><b><font color="#423330">Hiroshi
Misae
<font face="5yearsoldfont"><font color="#52548b"><b>Shinnosuke</b></font></font></font></b></font></font>

30
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:30,900
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Oh no! I forgot to buy the ground pork and radishes!</b></font>

31
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,920
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Now I've done it.</b></font>

32
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:39,080
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>We're out of soy sauce too!</b></font>

33
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:41,580
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Shoot! And I have my hands full at the moment.</b></font>

34
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:44,120
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What should I do?</b></font>

35
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:47,300
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Oh, I know!
I'll get Shinnosuke to go for me.</b></font>

36
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:50,050
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>He's never gone shopping by himself before,</b></font>

37
00:01:50,050 --> 00:01:51,540
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>so it'll be a good
experience for him.</b></font>

38
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:53,740
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Shinnosuke!</b></font>

39
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:54,940
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What?</b></font>

40
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,720
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Can you come here for a sec?</b></font>

41
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,970
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I can't right now. I'm drawing!</b></font>

42
00:01:58,970 --> 00:02:02,970
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b><i>What a defiant brat. I suppose I'll have to soft-soap him.</i></b></font>

43
00:02:02,970 --> 00:02:05,200
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Did it turn out nice?</b></font>

44
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,000
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Yeah!</b></font>

45
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,440
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I want to see it!</b></font>

46
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,140
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Sure!</b></font>

47
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:15,280
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Check it out. It's an elephant!</b></font>

48
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:19,360
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>An elephant, an elephant...</b></font>

49
00:02:20,060 --> 00:02:22,100
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b><i>He's such a fool.</i></b></font>

50
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:24,830
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I don't have time for this!{TLC}</b></font>

51
00:02:24,830 --> 00:02:28,660
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>And Mom... and Dad... {TLC - the elephant's mom and dad?}</b></font>

52
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:32,250
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Listen to me!
Put on some underwear!</b></font>

53
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:37,240
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I put on some underwear. What did you want?</b></font>

54
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,720
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Go shopping for me.</b></font>

55
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:42,200
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Do it yourself, Misae.</b></font>

56
00:02:42,930 --> 00:02:45,890
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>How many times have I told you not to imitate your father?</b></font>

57
00:02:45,890 --> 00:02:47,350
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I know, Misae.</b></font>

58
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:51,280
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Don't call your
parents by their names.</b></font>

59
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,320
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Yes, ma'am.</b></font>

60
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:55,840
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Tonight, your father is bringing home a very important client,</b></font>

61
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,700
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>so I'm making a special dinner.</b></font>

62
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:58,600
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I see.</b></font>

63
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:01,280
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>That's why I'm <i>so</i> busy.</b></font>

64
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,840
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>And I want you to help me out.</b></font>

65
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,660
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Will you go shopping for me?</b></font>

66
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,280
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Yeah, no problem!</b></font>

67
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:12,480
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Wait a minute!
Do you even know what to get?</b></font>

68
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,950
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Potato chips and a Okamoto Natsuki photo spread!</b></font>

69
00:03:15,950 --> 00:03:17,820
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>No!!</b></font>

70
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:20,850
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Listen closely. We need ground pork and radishes...</b></font>

71
00:03:20,850 --> 00:03:23,000
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>H-Hold on a second.
I need to take a mome.</b></font>

72
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,640
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You mean "memo," not "mome." I guess he is still just a kid.{TLC}</b></font>

