<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>It's your own fault.</b></font>

639
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:57,300
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You're crushing me.</b></font>

640
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:03,740
