645
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:25,850
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>No more sleeping!</b></font>

646
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,350
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Yeah, just like that.
Hurry up now.</b></font>

647
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:32,420
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Underwear... Underwear...</b></font>

648
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:38,030
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Pants... Pants...</b></font>

649
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,490
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>That's not right.</b></font>

650
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:44,950
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>All done.</b></font>

651
00:10:44,950 --> 00:10:47,580
