<font size="28"><font face="Calibri"><font color="#000000"><font size="22">Monthly <b><font face="Bee Marker Ink"><font color="#5c496e">Ikagawa</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

659
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,840
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Why are you taking
something like that?!</b></font>

660
00:10:56,840 --> 00:11:00,300
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>That doesn't need to be in there!</b></font>

661
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:05,410
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay, pack your tissues and handkerchief.</b></font>

662
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,270
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Done.</b></font>

663
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:16,080
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hey, hold on!</b></font>

664
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:21,160
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>This isn't a handkerchief!</b></font>

665
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:26,120
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Here, wash your face with some cold water. It'll wake you up.</b></font>

666
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:30,560
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Quickly wash up.</b></font>

667
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,260
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay...</b></font>

668
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,260
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I've got a bad feeling...</b></font>

669
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,260
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I knew it!</b></font>

670
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:49,680
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Feel the wrath of my triple punch of anger! {TLC - wat}</b></font>

