00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:17,670
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>But you haven't even started. {TLC - don't know how to translate this more literally}</b></font>

682
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:27,220
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You changed the soup, didn't you?</b></font>

683
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,850
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Never mind that. Hurry up!</b></font>

684
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,140
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'll eat this.</b></font>

685
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:39,730
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>These are no ordinary bean.</b></font>

686
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,780
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>They are just normal beans.</b></font>

687
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:43,620
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Did you steal them?</b></font>

688
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:46,340
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Why would you think I stole them?!</b></font>

689
00:12:46,340 --> 00:12:47,560
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Then you bought them?</b></font>

690
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:48,900
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Of course I did!</b></font>

691
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:51,780
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Then they aren't just normal beans. {TLC - pun for free}</b></font>

692
00:12:52,660 --> 00:12:55,120
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Just hurry up and eat!</b></font>

693
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:13,680
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'm an idiot for giving him beans.</b></font>

694
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:17,040
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You look depressed, Misae.</b></font>

695
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,720
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hurry up!</b></font>

696
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,260
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Did you brush your teeth?</b></font>

697
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:22,840
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I did.</b></font>

698
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,660
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Did you go pee?</b></font>

699
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:24,120
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I did.</b></font>

700
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:24,840
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Did you poop?</b></font>

701
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,160
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I didn't.</b></font>

702
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,480
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hurry up now.</b></font>

703
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,540
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>The bus is here to pick you up.</b></font>

704
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:32,440
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Oh, I don't have my hat...</b></font>

705
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,100
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hurry and go get it!</b></font>

706
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:36,720
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Here.</b></font>

707
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:40,140
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>If you don't make it
on the bus today,</b></font>

708
00:13:40,140 --> 00:13:42,050
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>it won't be the only
thing leaving you. {TLC}</b></font>

709
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:45,970
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I couldn't find it, so I'll use this.</b></font>

710
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:49,180
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You idiot!</b></font>

711
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,320
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Good morning, sensei!</b></font>

712
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,420
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Good morning!</b></font>

713
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:57,540
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Good afternoon!</b></font>

714
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:59,080
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You mean "good morning."</b></font>

715
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:03,530
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay, Shin-chan.
Why don't you get on the bus?</b></font>

716
00:14:03,530 --> 00:14:07,740
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay, whatever you say, Midori.</b></font>

717
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:17,880
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What's wrong, Shinnosuke?</b></font>

718
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,400
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I need to poop.</b></font>

719
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,920
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Just keep it in!</b></font>

720
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,380
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>A bit came out...</b></font>

721
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:33,020
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Go on without him.</b></font>

722
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:35,340
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'll bring him in later.</b></font>

723
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:36,810
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay...</b></font>

724
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:50,340
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>The bus fare...</b></font>

725
00:14:51,300 --> 00:14:53,660
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>The morning sun is radiant.</b></font>

726
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:58,920
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Shinnosuke had to poop, so we were late once again.</b></font>

