<font size="28"><font color="#979953">▲</font></font>

732
00:15:10,090 --> 00:15:15,010
<font size="28"><font color="#aa4c7c"><font size="80"><font face="Cabold Comic">Ooh</font></font></font></font>

733
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:15,010
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Ooh!</b></font>

734
00:15:15,010 --> 00:15:20,770
<font face="Brush Dom Regular" size="65" color="#5e5299"><font color="#3c791b"><font size="69">{\an1}Doodling</font></font></font>

735
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:19,120
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Doodling!</b></font>

736
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:24,660
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Good morning, sensei!</b></font>

737
00:15:24,660 --> 00:15:26,730
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Good morning!</b></font>

738
00:15:26,730 --> 00:15:28,820
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Today, we're going to doodle.</b></font>

739
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,700
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Did everyone bring their crayons?</b></font>

740
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:32,260
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Yes!</b></font>

741
00:15:32,260 --> 00:15:33,560
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay, then...</b></font>

742
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,540
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Shinnosuke-kun?</b></font>

743
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:40,720
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What's wrong? Are you okay?</b></font>

744
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:42,680
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I've got a nosebleed.</b></font>

745
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:47,000
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>If you keep doing that, you're going to have nose like a pig!</b></font>

746
00:15:48,180 --> 00:15:49,460
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Have you tried this, sensei?</b></font>

747
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:52,640
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Does it look like I have a pig nose?</b></font>

748
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:56,430
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b><i>Calm down, Midori. You shouldn't get so worked up over a kid.</i></b></font>

749
00:15:57,320 --> 00:16:00,930
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Shin-chan! This is the second time I've told you to stop playing around.</b></font>

750
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,650
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I've got a runny nose.</b></font>

751
00:16:05,940 --> 00:16:08,900
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I told you to stop!</b></font>

752
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:12,040
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Today, you can draw whatever you like.</b></font>

753
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:14,520
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Animals, flowers — anything is fine!</b></font>

754
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:15,380
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay!</b></font>

755
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:17,430
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What are you going to draw, Shin-chan?</b></font>

756
00:16:25,140 --> 00:16:26,460
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Where are you going, Shin-chan?</b></font>

757
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:29,960
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You want me to stay still?</b></font>

758
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:32,600
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hey, what are you
doing over there?</b></font>

759
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,520
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Drawing what I like.</b></font>

760
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:36,430
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You don't need to use a model.</b></font>

761
00:16:36,430 --> 00:16:41,040
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>A drawing is something you use your imagination to come up with on paper.</b></font>

762
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:41,850
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>My imagination?</b></font>

763
00:16:41,850 --> 00:16:46,400
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Yes! You close your eyes like this and draw whatever you see in your head.</b></font>

764
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:49,780
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Wow! I can see a beautiful flower garden!</b></font>

765
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:51,820
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Now you give it a try!</b></font>

766
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,430
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Yeah, just like that.</b></font>

767
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:56,780
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Oh!</b></font>

768
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:59,440
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Good! Now do you see anything?</b></font>

769
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:02,360
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I can't see anything except darkness.</b></font>

770
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:10,170
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay, let's see what kind of things you are all drawing!</b></font>

771
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,700
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You're drawing a flower, right, Nene-chan?</b></font>

772
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,130
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>That's right, Yoshinaga-sensei!</b></font>

773
00:17:14,460 --> 00:17:15,590
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>It's a beautiful flower.</b></font>

774
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:18,440
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I really tried hard to draw it.</b></font>

775
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,860
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Me too, sensei.</b></font>

776
00:17:20,860 --> 00:17:22,560
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'm a beautiful flower.</b></font>

777
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:24,520
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Quit with your nonsense.</b></font>

778
00:17:24,820 --> 00:17:26,180
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Nonsense?</b></font>

779
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:29,480
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Stop sticking crayons up your nose!</b></font>

780
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,730
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Okay.</b></font>

781
00:17:31,220 --> 00:17:33,840
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Masao-kun, what are you drawing?</b></font>

782
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:36,220
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Let me see it.</b></font>

783
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:38,870
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I-I'm not done with it yet.</b></font>

784
00:17:39,100 --> 00:17:41,660
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>That's fine!
Let me just take a peek then.</b></font>

785
00:17:41,660 --> 00:17:43,380
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>No. It's terrible!</b></font>

786
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:44,180
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'm sure it's fine.</b></font>

787
00:17:44,180 --> 00:17:45,830
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>No! It's really bad!</b></font>

788
00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:48,520
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I see...</b></font>

789
00:17:50,460 --> 00:17:51,750
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>It really is bad.</b></font>

790
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:55,080
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'm sorry, Masao-kun!</b></font>

791
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:56,800
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I shouldn't have done that.</b></font>

792
00:17:57,220 --> 00:17:58,380
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>You made him cry.</b></font>

793
00:17:58,380 --> 00:18:00,180
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hey now, I wasn't
the one who did it.</b></font>

794
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:04,140
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Bo-chan?</b></font>

795
00:18:05,540 --> 00:18:07,540
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Can I see your drawing?</b></font>

796
00:18:07,540 --> 00:18:08,600
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Sure.</b></font>

797
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:14,760
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Bo-chan, what is
this supposed to be?</b></font>

798
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,190
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Is it the sun?</b></font>

799
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:17,900
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>A ball.</b></font>

800
00:18:17,900 --> 00:18:19,870
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>O-Of course, it's a ball!</b></font>

801
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:21,900
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Nicely done.</b></font>

802
00:18:21,900 --> 00:18:23,900
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Even I could draw
something like that.</b></font>

803
00:18:23,900 --> 00:18:26,820
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>There's no point if you're just copying others.</b></font>

804
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,400
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Kazama-kun!</b></font>

805
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,790
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hey, Yoshinaga-sensei!</b></font>

806
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,720
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>So what did you draw?</b></font>

807
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:33,750
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'm not really confident in it.</b></font>

808
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:40,260
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Wow, you're very talented, Kazama-kun.</b></font>

809
00:18:40,260 --> 00:18:43,820
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I personally don't think I got the color of the sky quite right though.</b></font>

810
00:18:43,820 --> 00:18:45,340
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Let me see it too.</b></font>

811
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:46,600
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Hehe, he can see it.</b></font>

812
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:49,230
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>It's not like seeing it will make his any better.</b></font>

813
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:54,440
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What do you think of my skills?</b></font>

814
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:00,120
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What is it?</b></font>

815
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:05,040
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What's wrong with it?</b></font>

816
00:19:05,460 --> 00:19:07,680
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>There's no heart in this drawing.</b></font>

817
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:08,410
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>What?!</b></font>

818
00:19:08,600 --> 00:19:10,860
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>Are you nitpicking my drawing?!</b></font>

819
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:14,120
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>No, there's just no heart in it.</b></font>

820
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:15,340
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>I'll add some in.</b></font>

821
00:19:16,820 --> 00:19:21,130
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b><i>Could I have been the one to discover Shin-chan's artistic talent?</i></b></font>

822
00:19:21,380 --> 00:19:24,340
<font face="Segoe UI" size="36"><b>That's great, Shin-chan!
Try to put some heart into it!</b></font>

